Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Leigh Pierce <leighpierce@me.com>
Description: Monarch of Tone overdrive plugin (VST3)
 Circuit-level emulation of the Analog Man King of Tone dual-channel overdrive
 pedal, built with JUCE and chowdsp_wdf WDF circuit modelling.
